guest_message: Hi there! This is Amanda Foster. I'm looking to place an order for my team lunch. Can I get three Classic Burgers cooked medium, each with French fries? Also, I'd like to order two Caesar Salads with grilled chicken. Could you help with that?
No, drinks or desserts won't be necessary for today. Just the burgers and salads, thanks! Can you confirm the total price and delivery time, please?
Yes, that all sounds perfect! My contact number is 123-456-7890. Thanks so much for taking care of this. Looking forward to picking it up in about 20 minutes!
